# Buffer + Heatmap Combo - Harita Hive Analysis Tool
# MIT License
#
# Multi-buffer + live heatmap generator with export options
# Combines spatial buffering with density visualization
#
# Features:
# - Multiple buffer distances simultaneously
# - Real-time heatmap generation
# - Kernel density estimation
# - Customizable color schemes
# - Interactive parameter adjustment
# - High-resolution export options
#
# Buffer Types:
# - Fixed distance buffers
# - Variable distance by attribute
# - Multi-ring buffers
# - Dissolve vs. non-dissolve options
# - Custom buffer shapes
#
# Heatmap Algorithms:
# - Gaussian kernel density
# - Quartic kernel density
# - Triangular kernel density
# - Adaptive bandwidth selection
# - Point weight support
#
# Visualization Options:
# - Multiple color ramps
# - Transparency control
# - Contour line overlays
# - 3D surface rendering
# - Animation for temporal data
#
# Usage:
# buffer-heatmap --input points.shp --buffers 100,300,500 --heatmap-bandwidth auto
# buffer-heatmap --weighted-points crimes.shp --weight-field severity --animate